<h>'Blue Monday:' things just get better from here</h>
<p>Mondays are challenging at the best of times for many people, but one psychologist says the third Monday in January is the worst of the year.</p>
<p>The Blue Monday theory was developed by Welsh psychologist Cliff Arnall, who said a number of factors coincide to make it most down day.</p>
<p>Not all psychologists agree that the theory is credible, and a sampling of some people in Vancouver Monday found some support for the idea — while others were too busy enjoying themselves.</p>
